{% extends '_templates/base.njk' %}

{% block page_title %}Homepage{% endblock %}
{% block content %}
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <h1>Austin Tourism Guide</h1>
        <p>Years ago when people talked about Austin they would quickly mention the music. But that's just the beginning of what they're saying these days. Austin is also home to a wonderful ballet, world-class museums, one-of-a-kind shopping and beautiful outdoor spaces. You can just as easily spend your morning paddling the lake as you can strolling through a celebrated history museum. And it's okay if you don't have time to fit it all in, you can just come back and visit us again.</p>
        {% for tease in austin.landmarks %}
          <div class="card bg-dark col-sm-6 col-lg-4 mb-4" style="width: 18rem;">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="img/landmarks/{{ tease.image }}" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-text"><a href="landmarks/{{ tease.slug }}.html">{{ tease.name }}</a></h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
        <p>- Source: <a href="https://www.austintexas.org/things-to-do/" target="_blank">Visit Austin</a></p>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}